snippet.title: Diablo 3D Trailer *Expansion out Now!*
snippet.description:
2 years in the making, This Doom Total Conversion mod by iron Tusk, takes you to the world of Sanctuary, where you face off against burning hells, All your favorite places are there, runes, perfect gems, skills, and more! Requires Heretic.Wad to play!

 The New #Expansion Children of Hatred is Released and features new weapons, items, shrines, and monsters, as well as a return to the burning hells to face the ultimate foe and leader of the Triune, Lucion The Son of Mephisto. Enjoy the Trailer! Follow updates on the zdoom forums and The #Diablo 3D Facebook page for more!

#Zdoom: https://forum.zdoom.org/viewtopic.php?f=19&t=59198

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/irontuskDiablo3D

Mod
https://www.mediafire.com/file/tagpypjv8ls2aex/DIABLO_3D_VERSION_1.1.0_LITE.zip/file (Diablo 3D Lite Version) - 602MB Zip File
https://www.mediafire.com/file/ytzx42mp60bnklt/DIABLO_3D_VERSION_1.1.0_GODLY.zip/file (Diablo 3D Full Version) - 1.85GB Zip File
https://www.mediafire.com/file/3hecg2r5f6oef5p/Diablo_3D_1.1.2_patch.rar/file (DIABLO 3D 1.1.1 PATCH)
http://www.mediafire.com/file/0dfn6r2g56vke7c/Diablo_3D_Classic.zip/file (Diablo 3D Classic - VR Compatible) 1GB Zip file

Ratings are Disabled by Default.
